<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"  TextAlignment="Justify"   xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml">

<Paragraph>Essential Presentation library has support for adding notes in a PowerPoint presentation.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph>This sample demonstrates how to add and convert the notes pages of a PowerPoint slide.</Paragraph>

<BlockUIContainer>
<TextBlock Style="{DynamicResource HeaderTextStyle}"><Bold>Features:</Bold></TextBlock>
</BlockUIContainer>
<List>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Add, remove, and modify 'Notes Pages' in a PowerPoint slide.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Convert the 'Notes Pages' to PDF document.</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>

<Paragraph><Bold>Note:</Bold> This library supports creation, manipulation and conversion to PDF/image for .pptx format alone.</Paragraph>

